------ For Ag, you have to install ag in your host firstly.
	# OSX
	brew install the_silver_searcher
	# Archlinux
	pacman -S the_silver_searcher
	# Ubuntu
	apt-get install silversearcher-ag

------ cd .vim 
       git submodule init 
       git submodule update

------ At last, you have to create a soft link file .vimrc which links to .vim/.vimrc

